WEBVTT

01:43.170 --> 01:46.020
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.130 --> 01:49.009
[Episode 3]

01:49.090 --> 01:54.289
[Thank you for witnessing our wedding.]

01:50.140 --> 01:51.810
Not bad, Dalu.

01:52.110 --> 01:53.170
VP of a company?

01:53.610 --> 01:54.360
Don't mess with me.

01:54.380 --> 01:55.430
What VP?

01:55.550 --> 01:57.020
I'm just Zhong's minion.

01:57.190 --> 01:57.920
Who said that?

01:57.950 --> 01:59.270
Under Dalu's leadership,

01:59.289 --> 01:59.910
our company

01:59.940 --> 02:01.070
has been flourishing.

02:01.190 --> 02:01.760
Come visit

02:01.790 --> 02:03.270
when you have time.

02:03.290 --> 02:04.190
Come on!

02:04.750 --> 02:06.480
Welcome to my wedding!

02:06.500 --> 02:07.120
Come on!

02:07.150 --> 02:07.600
Here.

02:07.630 --> 02:08.360
Happy wedding!

02:08.910 --> 02:09.639
Um, sorry,

02:09.669 --> 02:10.270
this seat's taken.

02:10.289 --> 02:11.030
Oh, it's taken?

02:11.030 --> 02:11.580
Yes.

02:11.710 --> 02:12.650
I'm so sorry.

02:25.950 --> 02:26.880
You should see how

02:26.910 --> 02:27.800
Ding Jing's acting,

02:27.829 --> 02:29.360
like she's going to devour Jiang Chengyi.

02:29.470 --> 02:30.470
Don't you care?

02:30.500 --> 02:31.400
Let her.

02:31.430 --> 02:32.570
What does it have to do with me?

02:34.040 --> 02:34.840
Look at you.

02:35.200 --> 02:36.370
There's a seat there. Go there.

02:36.390 --> 02:36.870
Okay.

02:40.240 --> 02:41.060
Chengyi.

02:42.570 --> 02:43.579
Can I sit here?

02:50.560 --> 02:51.260
Lu Yan.

02:51.680 --> 02:52.150
Sit here.

02:52.650 --> 02:53.640
What are you waiting for?

02:53.670 --> 02:54.400
-Sit.
-Sit.

02:54.490 --> 02:54.950
Sure.

02:54.980 --> 02:56.350
I'll sit with those from my department.

03:01.620 --> 03:02.470
Honey.

03:02.490 --> 03:03.230
Long time no see.

03:03.230 --> 03:03.950
How've you been?

03:03.970 --> 03:05.040
I've been good.

03:05.190 --> 03:06.060
What about you?

03:09.690 --> 03:10.470
Want some chocolate?

03:12.710 --> 03:13.910
Thank you.

03:13.940 --> 03:15.640
Wen is such a nice senior.

03:15.830 --> 03:17.940
He specially kept one for Lu Yan.

03:18.030 --> 03:19.620
Wen has always been nice.

03:19.650 --> 03:20.530
He's nice to everyone,

03:20.560 --> 03:20.980
right?

03:21.010 --> 03:22.560
Considerate and caring.

03:24.440 --> 03:25.540
Why do you only have water?

03:26.120 --> 03:27.140
I can't drink.

03:29.100 --> 03:30.190
That's too bad.

03:30.200 --> 03:31.650
I wanted to drink with you.

03:32.040 --> 03:33.120
Come on!

03:33.150 --> 03:34.460
-Thank you! Come on!
-Come on!

03:34.480 --> 03:35.250
Happy wedding!

03:35.310 --> 03:36.470
-Have a baby soon!
-Thank you.

03:36.490 --> 03:36.930
Thank you.

03:36.960 --> 03:38.050
I like what I'm hearing.

03:38.070 --> 03:39.520
You guys hurry too.

03:39.550 --> 03:40.560
Fight for it.

03:41.060 --> 03:41.820
Wen.

03:41.850 --> 03:42.400
You are

03:42.430 --> 03:43.530
running a talent agency.

03:43.750 --> 03:44.550
Are all your artists

03:44.579 --> 03:46.260
stunning beauties?

03:46.290 --> 03:46.880
Yeah.

03:46.920 --> 03:47.950
Maybe it's a force of habit

03:47.980 --> 03:49.050
from when I was a doctor,

03:49.100 --> 03:50.410
but everyone looks the same to me.

03:53.240 --> 03:54.130
No way.

03:54.160 --> 03:55.450
Then don't you

03:55.660 --> 03:57.650
have anyone you like?

03:57.780 --> 03:59.210
Have you never been in a relationship?

03:59.800 --> 04:00.610
Not yet.

04:01.070 --> 04:02.020
I'll let you know

04:02.060 --> 04:02.930
if I'm dating anyone.

04:04.520 --> 04:05.940
So mysterious.

04:06.720 --> 04:07.730
I see. I see.

04:08.010 --> 04:09.090
Is the food okay?

04:09.560 --> 04:09.980
It's good.

04:09.980 --> 04:10.470
Very good.

04:10.470 --> 04:11.800
It's not cheap.

04:12.270 --> 04:13.020
I know, I know.

04:13.050 --> 04:13.930
We'll make a toast at that table.

04:13.960 --> 04:14.430
Go ahead and eat.

04:14.470 --> 04:14.920
Okay.

04:15.110 --> 04:16.050
Come on!

04:16.110 --> 04:17.110
Thank you so much for today.

04:17.140 --> 04:18.050
Happy wedding.

04:18.630 --> 04:19.680
Thank you!

04:19.720 --> 04:20.269
Always be happy!

04:20.269 --> 04:20.630
Thank you!

04:20.750 --> 04:21.790
Thank you, guys!

04:22.950 --> 04:24.080
Do you know

04:24.120 --> 04:25.980
a celebrity called

04:26.110 --> 04:26.990
Yu...

04:28.950 --> 04:29.610
Bo...

04:29.710 --> 04:30.570
-Yu Bofeng?
-Feng?

04:30.600 --> 04:31.350
Yes, yes.

04:31.390 --> 04:32.530
It's hard to pronounce.

04:33.240 --> 04:33.930
He's under our agency.

04:33.950 --> 04:35.100
He is?

04:35.120 --> 04:36.730
Let me show you his photos.

04:37.530 --> 04:38.770
It's not that I like him.

04:38.900 --> 04:39.970
It's...

04:40.030 --> 04:41.150
I have a friend,

04:41.170 --> 04:41.770
a close friend,

04:41.800 --> 04:42.650
who's a huge fan.

04:42.680 --> 04:44.100
She wants a, what's that called,

04:44.140 --> 04:45.450
an autographed...

04:45.470 --> 04:46.560
an autographed photo?

04:46.580 --> 04:47.210
With your friend's name on it?

04:47.320 --> 04:48.120
Yes, yes.

04:48.150 --> 04:48.710
No problem!

04:48.750 --> 04:49.430
With her name on it.

04:49.540 --> 04:50.909
Let me show you his photos.

04:50.930 --> 04:52.020
Yes, that's him.

04:52.440 --> 04:54.260
This is from a recent photoshoot.

04:54.670 --> 04:55.760
Do you prefer any?

04:55.790 --> 04:57.300
I'll get him to autograph it

04:57.430 --> 04:58.200
with your friend's name.

04:58.350 --> 04:59.250
Let me see.

04:59.950 --> 05:01.010
Why do I feel like

05:01.130 --> 05:01.950
you've changed

05:01.980 --> 05:03.090
in the past two years?

05:03.730 --> 05:05.170
I haven't.

05:06.320 --> 05:08.250
Maybe it's because

05:08.270 --> 05:10.010
you're working for

05:10.040 --> 05:11.260
the government now?

05:11.650 --> 05:13.310
You're different from your uni days.

05:14.470 --> 05:15.790
You...

05:17.440 --> 05:18.410
want to drink?

05:18.900 --> 05:20.060
Didn't you say you can't drink?

05:23.000 --> 05:23.780
Dalu!

05:24.340 --> 05:25.650
Have a drink with Ding Jing.

05:25.690 --> 05:26.550
I can't drink.

05:26.760 --> 05:27.380
No, wait,

05:27.430 --> 05:28.820
I don't have to drink.

05:28.820 --> 05:30.550
Princess Ding.

05:30.550 --> 05:31.240
He doesn't drink.

05:31.270 --> 05:32.020
The whole basketball team's here.

05:32.050 --> 05:33.470
We'll drink with you.

05:33.640 --> 05:34.740
Excel in your career?

05:34.770 --> 05:35.830
Can he write that much?

05:35.870 --> 05:36.370
Of course!

05:36.390 --> 05:37.710
How about we get her

05:37.750 --> 05:38.550
a bigger photo?

05:38.650 --> 05:39.440
Sure, sure.

05:39.460 --> 05:40.430
Thank you.

05:41.930 --> 05:42.790
Give me my glass.

05:42.810 --> 05:43.710
Have a drink.

05:44.980 --> 05:46.830
I'll text you her name.

05:47.650 --> 05:48.400
After

05:48.430 --> 05:49.570
he's autographed it,

05:49.590 --> 05:50.370
I'll send it to you.

05:50.400 --> 05:51.210
That's great!

05:51.230 --> 05:51.860
She is...

05:51.880 --> 05:53.550
Her name is Wang Qianqian.

05:54.530 --> 05:55.430
She loves him

05:55.460 --> 05:56.300
so much.

05:58.320 --> 05:59.050
What are you looking at?

06:00.080 --> 06:00.990
Nothing, just spacing out.

06:01.490 --> 06:02.230
Ex-girlfriend?

06:03.100 --> 06:04.070
Rekindled love?

06:04.480 --> 06:05.540
Cut it out.

06:05.840 --> 06:06.820
It was so long ago.

06:06.850 --> 06:07.560
Long forgotten.

06:11.270 --> 06:12.930
Do you remember that basketball game in uni?

06:13.760 --> 06:14.660
Which game?

06:14.970 --> 06:16.230
The one where you vomited?

06:18.140 --> 06:20.230
Can you not embarrass me like that?

06:20.680 --> 06:22.160
When our School of Engineering

06:22.180 --> 06:23.740
played against their School of Medicine.

06:25.240 --> 06:26.110
I remember.

06:27.000 --> 06:28.070
Do you want to watch it?

06:28.110 --> 06:28.970
I still have the video.

06:29.070 --> 06:29.670
You still have it?

06:29.670 --> 06:30.990
Of course I want to want it.

06:31.010 --> 06:32.340
I was so cool in that game.

06:32.400 --> 06:32.909
Wait, no.

06:33.210 --> 06:34.280
Zhong was the coolest.

06:35.380 --> 06:36.270
Oh, come on.

06:36.270 --> 06:37.900
Who's cooler than Jiang Chengyi?

06:38.000 --> 06:38.720
Honey.

06:39.050 --> 06:39.740
Of course,

06:40.010 --> 06:41.090
my hubby's up there too.

06:41.500 --> 06:42.860
Give me the remote control.

06:44.120 --> 06:45.190
I'll play it now.

06:49.560 --> 06:53.480
[May 13, 1998
7:40 p.m.]

06:53.909 --> 06:54.880
I'm sorry.

06:54.900 --> 06:56.020
I made a mistake.

06:59.690 --> 07:01.520
[Ninghai University] [Heart of Fire Basketball Competition]

07:02.110 --> 07:03.310
[School of Engineering, Ninghai University]

07:03.640 --> 07:05.160
[School of Medicine, Ninghai University]

07:05.240 --> 07:07.070
[Ninghai University] [Heart of Fire Basketball Competition]

07:09.560 --> 07:11.490
Isn't this the legendary game

07:11.580 --> 07:12.730
between Jiang Chengyi

07:12.750 --> 07:13.550
and Wen?

07:13.570 --> 07:14.150
Yeah!

07:14.670 --> 07:15.470
So handsome.

07:29.430 --> 07:30.760
You will lose the first half.

07:30.960 --> 07:32.050
You can't beat me.

07:31.910 --> 07:33.010
[Ninghai University] [Heart of Fire Basketball Competition]

07:37.340 --> 07:38.880
[Medicine] [Engineering]

07:37.750 --> 07:38.610
Nice shot!

07:39.390 --> 07:40.190
Nice shot!

07:40.270 --> 07:40.840
Nice shot!

07:40.870 --> 07:41.550
Nice shot!

07:42.430 --> 07:44.830
Go! Go! Go!

07:45.710 --> 07:46.750
Both Wen Peng and Jiang Chengyi

07:46.790 --> 07:47.350
are fierce today!

07:47.430 --> 07:48.130
Yeah!

07:48.230 --> 07:49.540
With them two,

07:49.620 --> 07:51.470
our school team can aim to win the city's

07:51.470 --> 07:52.880
University League this year.

07:52.900 --> 07:53.710
Coach Zhou.

07:53.740 --> 07:54.600
Am I right?

07:55.570 --> 07:56.500
Don't laugh!

07:57.530 --> 07:58.420
Defense! Defense!

07:58.470 --> 07:59.400
Back to defense!

08:03.030 --> 08:04.470
Score! Score!

08:04.560 --> 08:05.770
Score! Score!

08:08.000 --> 08:09.390
Jiang, he pushed me again!

08:09.560 --> 08:10.800
Again?

08:12.990 --> 08:14.060
Are you playing ball or starting a fight?

08:16.910 --> 08:17.710
Flagrant foul!

08:17.800 --> 08:18.860
What's wrong with you?

08:23.980 --> 08:24.940
No. 9 in blue—

08:24.970 --> 08:25.920
technical foul.

08:25.950 --> 08:26.660
First foul, one free throw.

08:26.680 --> 08:27.940
But they pushed us!

08:28.350 --> 08:29.880
First warning to the blue team's bench!

08:30.050 --> 08:30.630
Go back!

08:30.650 --> 08:31.650
Rubbish ref!

08:31.690 --> 08:32.100
Rubbish ref!

08:32.130 --> 08:32.840
Rubbish ref!

08:33.320 --> 08:34.270
Just you wait.

08:34.289 --> 08:35.590
Just play ball.

08:36.190 --> 08:38.970
Go! Go! Go!

08:39.070 --> 08:41.549
Go! Go!

08:44.550 --> 08:45.600
Don't play tricks.

08:50.240 --> 08:51.370
Defense!

08:51.390 --> 08:52.490
-Defense!
-Defense!

08:52.560 --> 08:53.280
Defense!

08:53.320 --> 08:54.180
Defense!

08:59.650 --> 09:00.620
Nice shot!

09:00.670 --> 09:01.830
-Nice shot!
-Nice shot!

09:17.740 --> 09:18.790
Nice shot!

09:18.630 --> 09:19.870
[Engineering]

09:31.790 --> 09:32.580
What's wrong?

09:33.360 --> 09:34.110
Not feeling well?

09:34.520 --> 09:35.860
I was hit a bit hard.

09:36.310 --> 09:37.110
Why's Wen Peng

09:37.130 --> 09:38.190
so aggressive today?

09:38.920 --> 09:39.970
So scary.

09:40.800 --> 09:41.780
Scary, my ass.

09:41.980 --> 09:42.950
We're in the lead.

09:43.180 --> 09:45.020
Do you dislike him?

09:45.300 --> 09:46.350
I could tell from

09:46.390 --> 09:47.330
our team training.

09:47.360 --> 09:48.370
Did he offend you?

09:49.130 --> 09:50.200
Are you blind?

09:50.220 --> 09:51.690
He's the one who's been

09:51.820 --> 09:52.750
coming at me.

09:53.970 --> 09:54.740
Then fight back.

10:01.900 --> 10:02.450
[Ninghai University] [Heart of Fire Basketball Competition]

10:04.500 --> 10:05.630
[Ninghai University] [Heart of Fire Basketball Competition]

10:16.290 --> 10:17.310
[Ninghai University] [Heart of Fire Basketball Competition]

10:19.480 --> 10:20.910
Who do you think is the best dancer?

10:21.260 --> 10:22.650
Who do you think is the best dancer?

10:41.890 --> 10:43.550
[Ninghai University] [Heart of Fire Basketball Competition]

11:00.360 --> 11:01.340
Jiang, look!

11:01.840 --> 11:02.760
The Yangko Dance!

11:03.240 --> 11:03.970
Why are they...

11:09.330 --> 11:10.490
[Ninghai University] [Heart of Fire Basketball Competition]

11:19.380 --> 11:22.490
♫Charging into the world, with you in my backseat♫

11:24.460 --> 11:27.670
♫Pretending not to care even though you're all I care about♫

11:29.580 --> 11:32.980
♫I couldn't tell you for some unknown reason♫

11:32.630 --> 11:33.460
Listen to me.

11:33.630 --> 11:35.310
Since the cheerleaders are here today,

11:34.460 --> 11:38.940
♫That I like you the way you are♫

11:35.340 --> 11:36.430
why don't we relive the old days,

11:36.470 --> 11:36.910
yeah?

11:36.930 --> 11:37.790
Yeah!

11:38.550 --> 11:40.540
[Thank you for witnessing our wedding.]

11:42.190 --> 11:42.970
Lu Yan.

11:43.090 --> 11:44.300
I still can't forget

11:44.330 --> 11:45.700
your unique cheerleading

11:45.720 --> 11:47.140
even until now.

11:47.270 --> 11:48.220
Oh, stop it.

11:48.410 --> 11:48.990
Honey.

11:49.020 --> 11:49.810
Show them your moves.

11:49.850 --> 11:50.900
What moves?

11:50.920 --> 11:51.490
Come on.

11:51.630 --> 11:53.460
-Come on!
-Come on!

11:55.180 --> 11:56.840
[Thank you for witnessing our wedding.]

11:55.770 --> 11:56.910
Cool it, guys!

11:56.950 --> 11:57.750
So mean.

11:57.770 --> 11:58.310
Come on!

11:58.310 --> 11:59.830
Fine! I remember everything.

12:00.670 --> 12:01.860
Trying to test me, huh?

12:01.890 --> 12:02.820
Let's go!

12:04.750 --> 12:06.750
Dance! Dance! Dance!

12:08.080 --> 12:09.120
Music!

12:09.190 --> 12:10.330
Music, please!

12:10.360 --> 12:11.860
Five, six, seven, eight.

12:22.030 --> 12:23.970
[Thank you for witnessing our wedding.]

12:34.110 --> 12:35.030
Jiang, join us.

12:35.060 --> 12:35.890
Come on. Quick.

12:36.270 --> 12:36.830
Quick.

12:36.850 --> 12:37.750
Come on.

12:37.780 --> 12:38.440
Your arms.

13:24.990 --> 13:26.020
Isn't that Deng Man?

13:26.050 --> 13:27.560
Why's her photo still in there?

13:27.580 --> 13:28.700
What's going on?

13:28.840 --> 13:29.900
But I deleted it.

13:46.170 --> 13:47.200
Are you okay?

13:50.480 --> 13:51.930
I-I'm fine. I'm fine.

13:51.950 --> 13:54.200
I-I'm going out f-for some fresh air.

13:54.340 --> 13:55.120
I'll go with you.

13:55.150 --> 13:55.960
No, it's okay.

14:00.960 --> 14:02.350
Why's her photo still in there?

14:04.350 --> 14:04.930
Didn't I ask you

14:04.960 --> 14:05.590
to delete the photo?

14:05.610 --> 14:06.610
I did!

14:06.670 --> 14:07.370
I don't know

14:07.390 --> 14:08.430
why it's still in there!

14:27.560 --> 14:28.300
Lu Yan!

14:32.650 --> 14:33.460
Are you okay?

14:36.590 --> 14:37.320
I'm fine.

14:37.350 --> 14:38.350
Thank you, Wen.

14:40.190 --> 14:41.220
Don't let it bother you.

14:41.250 --> 14:42.570
They couldn't have done it on purpose.

14:45.250 --> 14:45.940
Uh, let me...

14:47.190 --> 14:47.910
Let me give you a ride.

14:48.750 --> 14:49.310
No need.

14:49.310 --> 14:50.670
I-I want to be alone.

14:52.190 --> 14:52.870
Lu Yan.

14:55.760 --> 14:56.570
I'll send you back.

14:58.620 --> 15:00.170
I want to be alone for a bit.

15:01.130 --> 15:02.660
You shouldn't be alone now.

15:04.370 --> 15:05.140
I'll send her back.

15:06.230 --> 15:07.060
Thank you for your help.

16:17.270 --> 16:18.660
♫The day♫

16:19.760 --> 16:22.570
♫You barged into my world♫

16:23.870 --> 16:25.440
♫I knew there wouldn't be♫

16:26.180 --> 16:29.580
♫Anyone better than you♫

16:32.510 --> 16:34.200
♫Too bad♫

16:36.240 --> 16:38.220
♫I have no right to desire in my life♫

16:38.080 --> 16:38.950
It's here, yeah?

16:39.050 --> 16:40.840
♫I missed my chance with you♫

16:40.560 --> 16:41.360
Um...

16:42.060 --> 16:45.170
♫Can we blame it on fate?♫

16:42.740 --> 16:43.450
Are you okay?

16:45.950 --> 16:46.510
I'm fine.

16:47.120 --> 16:49.990
♫Love songs always warn us♫

16:50.850 --> 16:53.830
♫Never to believe in forever and ever♫

16:55.610 --> 16:58.750
♫I always go all out; my naivety's to blame♫

16:59.240 --> 17:02.790
♫Bear the pain and heartache♫

17:03.320 --> 17:06.140
♫Your kiss is♫

17:04.290 --> 17:04.960
Lu Yan!

17:07.569 --> 17:12.510
♫Indelibly tattooed in my heart♫

17:13.240 --> 17:17.050
♫Believing in the rekindling of love♫

17:14.180 --> 17:14.819
Put this on.

17:18.369 --> 17:21.680
♫You're closer than family♫

17:20.450 --> 17:21.170
Thank you.

17:21.550 --> 17:22.230
And...

17:22.339 --> 17:25.750
♫Yet more unfamiliar than strangers♫

17:25.930 --> 17:26.829
This is my number.

17:26.569 --> 17:30.060
♫Risking it all, only to be reciprocated with cruelty♫

17:27.109 --> 17:28.310
Call me if you need anything.

17:30.750 --> 17:31.990
I-I'm fine.

17:31.140 --> 17:33.310
♫Aren't I stupid?♫

17:32.690 --> 17:33.230
Take it.

17:34.240 --> 17:37.520
♫Someone who was once closer than family♫

17:38.470 --> 17:42.000
♫Must I give up my soul?♫

17:42.850 --> 17:48.520
♫I can never love anyone else again♫

17:48.690 --> 17:52.160
♫Don't fall for the sad eyes♫

17:52.670 --> 17:55.770
♫Don't let fate succeed♫

17:56.300 --> 17:58.090
♫We're all grown ups♫

17:58.970 --> 18:02.000
♫Transformation is a process♫

18:03.140 --> 18:05.420
♫I'd rather be covered in scars♫

18:06.490 --> 18:09.020
♫Than give up on the possibility of us♫

18:10.020 --> 18:13.240
♫You're closer than family♫

18:13.780 --> 18:16.730
♫Our love is practically doomed♫

18:17.550 --> 18:19.870
♫I'm not asking for anything profound♫

18:20.930 --> 18:24.720
♫I just want to love this one person♫

18:25.500 --> 18:29.070
♫Someone who was once closer than family♫

18:29.970 --> 18:33.500
♫From now on, until the end of time♫

18:34.930 --> 18:38.250
♫No blood ties, yet more important♫

18:39.250 --> 18:41.950
♫Than family♫

18:43.350 --> 18:47.580
♫The one I lay my heart bare to♫

18:47.080 --> 18:47.680
Yan.

18:47.710 --> 18:49.790
Look at that guy. He's so funny.

18:48.410 --> 18:52.580
♫My dear stranger♫

19:22.030 --> 19:23.870
W-What are you looking at?

19:24.560 --> 19:25.380
Nothing.

19:26.630 --> 19:27.890
Are you sure?

19:29.350 --> 19:30.310
Nothing, really.

19:31.680 --> 19:32.690
I saw everything.

19:35.070 --> 19:35.690
Deng Man.

19:37.070 --> 19:38.660
Do you see me as a friend?

19:45.670 --> 19:46.820
I like Jiang Chengyi.

19:50.130 --> 19:50.740
Yan!

19:52.470 --> 19:53.460
Can you

19:54.140 --> 19:55.430
give me a chance?

19:56.070 --> 19:57.590
If you really like him that much,

19:57.620 --> 19:59.300
tell him yourself.

20:01.710 --> 20:03.110
I won't break up with him.

20:05.180 --> 20:06.540
Have you seen Man?

20:07.380 --> 20:08.220
No.

20:08.390 --> 20:10.180
She's not answering my calls.

20:10.490 --> 20:11.450
I'll try calling her.

20:12.700 --> 20:13.410
Sorry.

20:13.430 --> 20:14.990
The subscriber's phone is switched off.

20:14.990 --> 20:15.710
Switched off?

20:15.990 --> 20:17.270
Please try again later.

20:19.400 --> 20:20.610
Hello, Mr. Chen.

20:20.630 --> 20:21.710
Hello, is this Lu Yan?

20:22.290 --> 20:22.880
Yes.

20:23.230 --> 20:24.900
Is Deng Man from your dorm?

20:25.990 --> 20:26.830
Yes.

20:28.190 --> 20:28.910
What's the matter?

20:56.550 --> 21:01.140
[Strictly confidential
No photos or videos allowed]

21:16.570 --> 21:21.660
[Strictly confidential
No photos or videos allowed]

21:32.330 --> 21:33.220
Lu Yan!

21:35.030 --> 21:35.730
Lu Yan.

21:40.360 --> 21:41.490
Why do you want to break up?

21:47.580 --> 21:48.190
Say something.

21:52.680 --> 21:53.380
We are...

21:54.280 --> 21:55.200
not a good match.

21:55.790 --> 21:56.590
Not a good match?

22:48.670 --> 22:50.550
I clearly deleted it.

22:50.570 --> 22:51.230
She did.

22:51.270 --> 22:51.830
How is it?

22:52.410 --> 22:53.740
I just asked the hotel manager.

22:53.770 --> 22:55.050
They said there were too many guests

22:55.070 --> 22:56.530
and they didn't notice anyone suspicious.

22:58.100 --> 22:59.290
What happened then?

22:59.310 --> 23:00.080
I saw Zhen delete it

23:00.110 --> 23:01.140
with my own two eyes.

23:01.170 --> 23:02.010
How did it show up?

23:02.030 --> 23:03.590
I deleted it as soon as you told me to.

23:03.620 --> 23:04.940
Honey, don't worry.

23:05.040 --> 23:06.110
Maybe Zhen was too busy

23:06.130 --> 23:06.970
and didn't delete it properly.

23:09.940 --> 23:10.730
It's all my fault.

23:10.980 --> 23:11.670
I hope Lu Yan

23:11.670 --> 23:12.560
is okay.

23:12.760 --> 23:13.350
No,

23:13.380 --> 23:13.870
it's my fault.

23:14.460 --> 23:15.070
I should've

23:15.070 --> 23:16.250
checked one last time.

23:16.280 --> 23:17.250
What a way to ruin

23:17.280 --> 23:18.030
our wedding.

23:18.070 --> 23:19.320
Let's get married again.

23:22.040 --> 23:23.160
Forget it.

23:23.360 --> 23:23.810
It's okay.

23:23.840 --> 23:24.600
Guys, go home.

23:24.630 --> 23:25.560
You've been busy all day.

23:26.230 --> 23:27.470
You guys should go back too.

23:27.510 --> 23:28.240
Thank you for today.

23:28.570 --> 23:29.640
We'll be off then.

23:30.400 --> 23:30.950
See you, Sister-in-law.

23:30.970 --> 23:31.670
See you, Sister-in-law.

23:31.830 --> 23:32.510
Thank you.

23:32.530 --> 23:33.320
Thank you.

23:52.050 --> 23:52.780
Jiang.

23:52.960 --> 23:53.520
Zhong.

23:53.930 --> 23:55.610
Did you find out who did it?

23:55.840 --> 23:57.480
Dalu asked the manager on duty.

23:57.510 --> 23:58.970
There were too many guests today.

23:58.990 --> 23:59.920
Even I can't remember

23:59.950 --> 24:00.920
everyone who came.

24:01.250 --> 24:01.850
Okay.

24:01.870 --> 24:02.870
Leave my number

24:02.870 --> 24:04.230
with the manager.

24:04.770 --> 24:06.280
Get him to call me if he remembers anything.

24:06.700 --> 24:07.300
Okay.

24:07.830 --> 24:08.490
Tang Jie.

24:09.380 --> 24:10.610
Please spend more time with Lu Yan

24:10.640 --> 24:11.700
for the time being.

24:11.970 --> 24:13.390
I'm worried about her.

24:13.470 --> 24:14.270
Don't worry.

24:14.300 --> 24:15.790
I know what to do.

24:16.080 --> 24:17.490
Let me apologize to you two.

24:17.530 --> 24:19.220
I'm really sorry about today.

24:20.170 --> 24:21.590
I'll stay all the way the next time.

24:21.620 --> 24:23.330
Okay, come next time.

24:24.080 --> 24:25.090
Next time?

24:26.110 --> 24:26.850
I'm hanging up.

24:27.580 --> 24:28.530
With whom next time?

24:30.200 --> 24:31.920
Next time...

24:32.360 --> 24:34.070
His surname's Zhong too.

24:36.820 --> 24:37.630
Don't overthink it.

24:37.830 --> 24:38.890
Let's go home and rest.

24:39.570 --> 24:40.640
You must be exhausted.

24:44.100 --> 24:44.980
Jing!

24:45.540 --> 24:46.460
Why did you

24:46.480 --> 24:47.680
drink so much today?

24:52.810 --> 24:53.980
Here, have some water.

24:57.150 --> 24:57.970
Why did

24:58.140 --> 24:59.270
Deng Man's photo

24:59.270 --> 25:00.790
appear suddenly?

25:03.910 --> 25:12.350
[Restroom]

25:03.970 --> 25:05.700
Why don't I take you home?

25:05.830 --> 25:06.310
You...

25:06.330 --> 25:07.430
Wait a minute.

25:07.560 --> 25:08.740
Get me some tissues.

25:09.750 --> 25:11.020
Okay. Hang on.

25:24.680 --> 25:28.980
[Restroom]

25:41.120 --> 25:42.040
Are you okay?

25:50.310 --> 25:51.520
Don't drink too much next time.

25:53.080 --> 25:55.140
[Restroom]

26:00.670 --> 26:01.270
Here.

26:07.170 --> 26:09.130
Was that Wen?

26:10.040 --> 26:10.840
I heard

26:10.860 --> 26:11.600
that he runs

26:11.640 --> 26:13.180
a talent agency now.

26:13.830 --> 26:15.210
He's rich and handsome.

26:16.650 --> 26:17.560
If only I had

26:17.580 --> 26:19.010
gotten close with him in school.

27:09.810 --> 27:10.530
Goodness.

27:10.560 --> 27:11.800
You finally answered.

27:13.720 --> 27:14.430
What's wrong?

27:14.800 --> 27:16.070
Get to the hospital now.

27:16.100 --> 27:17.510
There's another epidural hematoma.

27:17.680 --> 27:18.920
I'm super swamped.

27:20.570 --> 27:21.230
Okay.

27:21.860 --> 27:22.930
I'll be right there.

28:32.830 --> 28:33.790
I'm so sorry!

28:33.810 --> 28:34.740
Sorry.

28:34.960 --> 28:36.030
Let me help you up.

28:36.070 --> 28:37.050
Are you hurt?

28:37.390 --> 28:38.600
Come with me.

28:38.680 --> 28:40.030
The hospital is just ahead.

29:28.190 --> 29:29.190
I...

29:29.960 --> 29:32.060
will never

29:32.800 --> 29:34.460
forgive you.

29:48.230 --> 29:48.950
Yan.

29:49.110 --> 29:50.540
That ER patient isn't coming anymore.

29:50.910 --> 29:52.260
If you haven't left home,

29:52.300 --> 29:53.210
you don't have to come.

30:56.500 --> 30:58.630
[I hate you!]

31:01.700 --> 31:02.180
[I hate you!]

31:02.180 --> 31:04.380
[I hate you! I'll curse you!]

31:06.950 --> 31:08.870
I will never forgive you.

31:21.590 --> 31:22.820
I knew you were—

31:24.000 --> 31:24.790
What's wrong, Yan?

31:25.810 --> 31:26.430
What's wrong?

31:26.790 --> 31:27.950
D-Do you have a fever?

31:27.970 --> 31:29.460
-No, no.
-Why are you covered in sweat?

31:29.840 --> 31:31.030
I just didn't sleep well.

31:32.320 --> 31:33.270
You didn't sleep well?

31:34.800 --> 31:35.840
Did Dr. Huang

31:35.880 --> 31:37.260
call you here late at night again?

31:39.000 --> 31:40.180
He's so annoying.

31:40.210 --> 31:41.230
You're not the one on duty,

31:41.250 --> 31:42.160
but he always does this.

31:42.200 --> 31:42.640
He...

31:43.130 --> 31:44.090
It's okay.

31:44.150 --> 31:45.250
I live nearby.

31:45.350 --> 31:46.070
How is it okay?

31:46.090 --> 31:46.740
If you keep doing this,

31:46.770 --> 31:47.860
you'll collapse.

31:47.880 --> 31:48.280
You...

31:49.720 --> 31:50.990
What are you doing?

31:51.820 --> 31:52.750
Stop typing.

31:52.780 --> 31:53.610
Look at the time!

31:53.640 --> 31:54.270
It's past twelve!

31:54.290 --> 31:55.050
Let's eat. Let's go.

31:55.320 --> 31:56.270
No need. I'm not hungry.

31:56.290 --> 31:57.590
What do you mean? Hurry.

31:57.610 --> 31:58.850
Food fuels the body.

31:58.880 --> 31:59.790
Never skip meals.

31:59.810 --> 32:00.700
You don't sleep or eat.

32:00.640 --> 32:03.870
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

32:00.730 --> 32:01.790
W-What should I do about you?

32:01.810 --> 32:02.640
Are you immortal?

32:03.780 --> 32:04.970
Captain Jiang?

32:06.280 --> 32:07.060
Dr. Lu.

32:07.750 --> 32:08.350
Are you busy?

32:08.570 --> 32:09.620
Can I speak to you for a minute?

32:10.940 --> 32:13.220
Is it about a patient?

32:14.640 --> 32:15.350
Yes.

32:16.810 --> 32:17.380
Well,

32:17.410 --> 32:18.770
you can talk while eating.

32:18.980 --> 32:20.310
She was on her way to lunch.

32:20.340 --> 32:22.040
You two can go together.

32:22.120 --> 32:23.310
Aren't we eating together?

32:23.330 --> 32:24.080
But...

32:27.320 --> 32:28.050
Sorry, sorry.

32:28.080 --> 32:29.160
My boyfriend's checking up on me.

32:29.190 --> 32:30.230
I can't go with you.

32:30.810 --> 32:31.740
You two go ahead.

32:31.790 --> 32:32.500
Bye.

32:32.420 --> 32:33.960
[Operating Area]

32:36.290 --> 32:37.120
Let's talk outside.

32:50.210 --> 32:51.200
What happened...

32:51.580 --> 32:52.470
to your hand?

32:57.680 --> 33:00.050
The alley in my neighborhood

33:00.270 --> 33:01.380
was too dark.

33:02.710 --> 33:04.270
I bumped into someone

33:04.270 --> 33:04.790
and got scratched.

33:05.350 --> 33:06.370
Only your hand's hurt?

33:06.740 --> 33:07.180
Yeah.

33:07.200 --> 33:08.130
W-What's the matter?

33:09.600 --> 33:11.150
Nothing, I wanted to talk...

33:12.080 --> 33:13.880
about my dad's

33:13.990 --> 33:14.990
condition.

33:15.960 --> 33:17.570
Your dad's condition?

33:17.610 --> 33:19.720
Didn't I explain everything last time?

33:22.350 --> 33:23.010
Right...

33:28.560 --> 33:29.370
Are you...

33:31.230 --> 33:32.160
Are you okay?

33:35.220 --> 33:35.920
I'm fine.

33:36.820 --> 33:37.990
I'm just...

33:42.110 --> 33:43.610
a bit worried about you.

33:46.860 --> 33:47.970
I'm doing okay.

33:49.220 --> 33:50.300
I didn't think

33:50.680 --> 33:52.330
that after so many years,

33:53.880 --> 33:55.680
you'd still be triggered

33:55.720 --> 33:56.550
by Deng Man's photo—

33:56.550 --> 33:57.150
Captain Jiang.

33:58.400 --> 33:59.920
Can you not bring that up?

34:00.470 --> 34:02.060
And I don't need your comfort.

34:04.690 --> 34:05.500
I...

34:06.140 --> 34:07.160
I have patients to take care of.

34:07.200 --> 34:07.880
I'll get going.

34:09.199 --> 34:09.940
Lu Yan.
